<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="title" content="My DevOps Portfolio" />
  <meta name="description" content="Explore real-world DevOps projects built with Flask, Kubernetes, Terraform, Jenkins, and more." />
  <title>My DevOps Journey</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Helvetica+Neue:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #fff;
      color: #000;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    header {
      background: #000;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin: 0;
    }
    header p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #ccc;
    }
    section {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    ul li::before {
      content: '✔';
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
      color: green;
    }
    .project-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    footer {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .social a {
      margin: 0 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #0077b5;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>My DevOps Journey</h1>
    <p>DevOps Engineer | Cloud-Native Enthusiast | Automation Addict</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <div class="project-icon">⿡</div>
    <h2>Flask Web App + CI/CD</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Build a Python Flask app</li>
      <li>Test it automatically</li>
      <li>Deploy using Jenkins + AWS</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="project-icon">⿢</div>
    <h2>Microservices with Docker</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Break monolithic app into microservices</li>
      <li>Use Docker & Docker Compose</li>
      <li>Add Redis caching + PostgreSQL database</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="project-icon">⿣</div>
    <h2>Kubernetes Deployment</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Set up Kubernetes on AWS</li>
      <li>Deploy apps with auto-scaling & load balancing</li>
      <li>Monitor your cluster</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="project-icon">⿤</div>
    <h2>Infrastructure as Code with Terraform</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Automate AWS infrastructure</li>
      <li>Create VPC, EC2, S3 using Terraform</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="project-icon">⿥</div>
    <h2>Monitoring & Alerting System</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Use Prometheus + Grafana for monitoring</li>
      <li>ELK Stack for logs</li>
      <li>Set up alerts like real production systems</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="project-icon">⿦</div>
    <h2>Complete DevOps Pipeline</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Integrate everything you built</li>
      <li>Use GitOps & ArgoCD</li>
      <li>Add security scanning, backups, and blue-green deployments</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="project-icon">⿧</div>
    <h2>ML Model Deployment Pipeline</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Deploy ML models with Flask API + Streamlit</li>
      <li>Containerize & deploy on Kubernetes</li>
      <li>Monitor ML models and set up A/B testing</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <h3>Connect with Me</h3>
    <div class="social">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/uditrajparihar/">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/uditrajparihar">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
